<table border=0 cellpadding=5 width="100%" class='ubut'><tr><td width=150 valign=top><div class='bsmall'><a name="c1212067756"><b>Forum Post</b></a><br><b>05/29/08 09:29</b><br><div style='font-size: 12pt;'><b><b>Jack & Sue</b></b></div><br></div></td><td valign=top><h2>ATM/credit cards</h2>Hi, <p>We will be driving from Panama City to Bocas in Nov. are there atm machines that we can use to get cash out, so we do not have to carry a lot of cash. We rarley even carry cash where we live in Miami. Also can we use credit cards?<p>Thanks we are excited about exploring Panama<p>
